pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "#FFFFFF"
elements:
  - elementId: nav-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 24, 200, 22]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>02 / Guiding Principle</p>
  - elementId: heading
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 60, 700, 42]
    content:
      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Guiding Principle</strong></p>
  - elementId: accent-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 112, 80, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: formula-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 150, 1160, 100]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"
  - elementId: formula-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 160, 1120, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Business Need <span style="color:#3B82F6;">→</span> AI Orchestrator <span style="color:#3B82F6;">→</span> AutoCAD/Revit <span style="color:#3B82F6;">→</span> Quality Control <span style="color:#3B82F6;">→</span> Digital Twin Platform <span style="color:#3B82F6;">→</span> Decision <span style="color:#3B82F6;">→</span> New Version</p>
  - elementId: principle-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 280, 1160, 140]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#F1F5F9"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 2
      color: "#3B82F6"
  - elementId: principle-quote
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 310, 1080, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [center, middle]
      text: |
        <p><em>"AI prepares, humans decide, the lead visualizes and modifies."</em></p>
  - elementId: explanation-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 460, 300, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>What this means</strong></p>
  - elementId: explanation-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 500, 1160, 160]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>The AI is <strong>not a replacement</strong> for designers — it is a <span style="color:$text;">production accelerator</span> and <span style="color:$text;">quality standardizer</span>.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">The two designers become the <strong>business validators</strong> and <strong>supervisors</strong> of the AI system.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">The project lead can explore, understand, and request changes without ever opening AutoCAD or Revit.</p>
